Notes: Commonwealth Conference game; Elizabethtown wins 1,000th game in program
history. First D3 women's team to reach the milestone and just the third in
all NCAA divisions (Tennessee and Louisiana Tech).
Game.Officials: Mark Behrens,  Karleena Tobin,  Joe Maurer
